title: The Return: Dean Wilson
excerpt: Dean Wilson to return at Anaheim 1.
author: Lewis Phillips
content:
Subscribe to MX Vice on YouTube.

Follow @MXVice on Instagram.

Dean Wilson is in for Anaheim 1! The first round of 2020 Monster Energy Supercross, which will be run at Angel Stadium in Southern California this weekend, has received a boost in the form of an entry from #15. It was just two months ago that Wilson left the Monster Energy Cup on a stretcher with a dislocated hip, yet now he is back on his FC 450 and ready to hit the track on Saturday night. How did things turn around so quickly? Wilson explained everything after spinning some laps at the private KTM/Husqvarna test track in Southern California earlier this week.
